	(text "Negotiation resistors are already inside the chip on the cc lines. \n\nUSB 2.0 can do 5V@500mA\nUSB 3.0 can do 5V@900mA\n\nUSB can already negotiate power through CC pins. \nBy selecting prescribed pull down resistors.\n\nThis IC provides more versatility. It is: \nIt is programmable through i2c, \nhandles faults\ncompatible with adapters\nnegotiation\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 306.832 40.386 0)
